# Beauty Boutique – Premium Makeup Store Documentation

This file provides an overview of the project, its features, setup instructions, and usage guidelines. For the full README, see `README.md` in the project root.

## 📁 Project Structure
```
make upo app/
├─ index.html            # Main page markup
├─ styles.css            # Global styles (pink theme, glassmorphism, animations)
├─ index.js              # Core JavaScript – product loading, cart logic, checkout
├─ README.md             # Comprehensive project documentation
├─ assets/               # Images, icons, and UI assets
│   ├─ product‑images/   # All product pictures
│   └─ logo/…
